#: src/tools/overview.md:3
msgid ""
"**Tools** are the agent's hands. A tool is a capability the model can invoke "
"mid-conversation — run a shell command, fetch an HTTP URL, extract a PDF, "
"open a browser, write a file, read a sensor. Every tool call is subject to "
"[security policy](../security/overview.md) and produces a [tool receipt](../"
"security/tool-receipts.md)."
