msgstr ""

#: src/foundations/fnd-001-intentional-architecture.md:61
msgid "**Vision**"
msgstr ""

#: src/foundations/fnd-001-intentional-architecture.md:61
msgid ""
"_Why does this project exist? Who is it for? What does success look like?_"
msgstr ""

#: src/foundations/fnd-001-intentional-architecture.md:61
msgid "You build things nobody needs, or contradict yourself across releases"
msgstr ""

#: src/foundations/fnd-001-intentional-architecture.md:62
msgid "**Architecture**"
msgstr ""

#: src/foundations/fnd-001-intentional-architecture.md:62
msgid "_What are the structural decisions that make the vision possible?_"
msgstr ""

#: src/foundations/fnd-001-intentional-architecture.md:62
msgid ""
"You end up with a \"Big Ball of Mud\" — code that works but cannot be "
"changed without breaking something else"
msgstr ""

#: src/foundations/fnd-001-intentional-architecture.md:63
msgid "**Design**"
msgstr ""

#: src/foundations/fnd-001-intentional-architecture.md:63
msgid "_How do the components relate? What are the interfaces between them?_"
msgstr ""

#: src/foundations/fnd-001-intentional-architecture.md:63
msgid ""
"You get tight coupling — components that know too much about each other's "
"internals"
msgstr ""

