msgid ""
"**What is in the kernel binary** — fixed at compile time, determined per "
"platform, published to GitHub Releases"
msgstr ""

#: src/foundations/fnd-001-intentional-architecture.md:326
msgid ""
"**What capabilities are available** — determined at runtime by which plugins "
"are installed via `zeroclaw plugin install`"
msgstr ""

#: src/foundations/fnd-001-intentional-architecture.md:328
msgid ""
"These are no longer the same question, and the current `[features]` section "
"of `Cargo.toml` must be interpreted through that lens."
