#: src/foundations/fnd-001-intentional-architecture.md:774
msgid ""
"The project's vision is expressed in runtime terms: **\\<5 MB RAM** on $10 "
"hardware. Binary size on disk and runtime memory footprint (RSS) are related "
"but not identical — demand paging means only executed code paths are "
"resident. Both are tracked."
