#: src/foundations/fnd-001-intentional-architecture.md:776
msgid ""
"**Two-pass model:** Architectural decomposition (Phases 1–3) and binary size "
"optimization are separate workstreams. Decomposition _enables_ optimization "
"by isolating dependencies to their owning crates. Maximizing efficiency "
"crate-by-crate is the expected second pass, not a deliverable of the "
"structural work itself."
