#: src/foundations/fnd-003-governance.md:268
msgid "Vote on RFCs with binding authority"
msgstr ""

#: src/foundations/fnd-003-governance.md:272
msgid "**Tier 2: Contributor**"
msgstr ""

#: src/foundations/fnd-003-governance.md:274
msgid ""
"Community members who have had at least two PRs merged into the `master` "
"branch."
msgstr ""

#: src/foundations/fnd-003-governance.md:276
